# MarshalStream.RemoveReadProcessor method

Unregisters a read processor.

```csharp
public bool RemoveReadProcessor(IMarshalStreamProcessor processor)
```

| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| processor | The read processor to unregister. |

## Return Value

`true` if the read processor was successfully unregistered; `false` if the read processor was not registered.
